items.description: Become the most fashionable guest at any dinner party, business meeting or funeral by mastering the amusing art of Hypnosis.
items.name: The "Hypnotize" Action
items.webDescription1: Become the most fashionable guest at any dinner party, business meeting or funeral by mastering the amusing art of Hypnosis.

items.description: The perfect response when you’re lost for words, can’t be bothered, or when you want to feign indifference to vicious, heartbreaking taunts.
items.name: The "Shrug" Reaction
items.webDescription1: The perfect response when you’re lost for words, can’t be bothered, or when you want to feign indifference to vicious, heartbreaking taunts.

items.description: Caught wind of some dinner cooking, fine perfume, or something deceased in the distance? Show off your keen sense of smell and take it all in.
items.name: The "Sniff" Reaction
items.webDescription1: Caught wind of some dinner cooking, fine perfume, or something deceased in the distance? Show off your keen sense of smell and take it all in.

items.description: Whether you are thanking your stars, have narrowly escaped death or wishing for luck at cards, muster your faith and pray to the powers that be.
items.name: The "Prayer" Action
items.webDescription1: Whether you are thanking your stars, have narrowly escaped death or wishing for luck at cards, muster your faith and pray to the powers that be.

items.description: Is the conversation getting tedious? This will surely do the trick. Casually flaunt that expensive watch and convey you belong in a place with a higher class of people.
items.name: The "Check the Time" Action
items.webDescription1: Is the conversation getting tedious? This will surely do the trick. Casually flaunt that expensive watch and convey you belong in a place with a higher class of people.

items.description: Prove that you’re wild, bordering on lunacy, or a capable lover, by growling and clawing at those nearby. Nothing demonstrates your animal instincts like pretending to be one.
items.name: The "Cougar Snarl" Taunt
items.webDescription1: Prove that you’re wild, bordering on lunacy, or a capable lover, by growling and clawing at those nearby. Nothing demonstrates your animal instincts like pretending to be one.

items.description: You know quality when you see it or, at the very least, when you bite it. Don’t be swindled. Check that your coins are genuine.
items.name: The "Coin Bite" Action
items.webDescription1: You know quality when you see it or, at the very least, when you bite it. Don’t be swindled. Check that your coins are genuine.

items.description: Want to celebrate in a way that is both fun and violent? Try firing dual pistols into the air.
items.name: The "Shoot the Sky" Action
items.webDescription1: Want to celebrate in a way that is both fun and violent? Try firing dual pistols into the air.

items.description: Feign incredulity or humbleness when the attention’s on you. Or, after handily defeating an opponent, mock them with this gesture and watch the rage volcano.
items.name: The "Who, Me?" Reaction
items.webDescription1: Feign incredulity or humbleness when the attention’s on you. Or, after handily defeating an opponent, mock them with this gesture and watch the rage volcano.

items.description: Nothing lightens the soul crushing burden of life like yielding to a tantrum. Unleash your frustration in a burst of rage.
items.name: The "Hissy Fit" Action
items.webDescription1: Nothing lightens the soul crushing burden of life like yielding to a tantrum. Unleash your frustration in a burst of rage.

items.description: Those who are decedents of good breeding know that refined social behavior begins with a fancy bow and flourish. Take credit for your superior stature with this highly expressive move.
items.name: The "Fancy Bow" Greet
items.webDescription1: Those who are decedents of good breeding know that refined social behavior begins with a fancy bow and flourish. Take credit for your superior stature with this highly expressive move.

items.description: Mockery reigns supreme as you needle, ridicule and tease an opponent into a deep pit of shame in which they may never recover.
items.name: The "Point and Laugh" Reaction
items.webDescription1: Mockery reigns supreme as you needle, ridicule and tease an opponent into a deep pit of shame in which they may never recover.

items.description: When you’re impressed and want to show gratitude, give a round of enthusiastic applause.
items.name: The "Applause" Reaction
items.webDescription1: When you’re impressed and want to show gratitude, give a round of enthusiastic applause.

items.description: Express your disappointment in the clearest way; with a downturned thumb and a frown.
items.name: The "Thumbs Down" Reaction
items.webDescription1: Express your disappointment in the clearest way; with a downturned thumb and a frown.

items.description: Implant a sense of inevitable doom with this vicious and fearsome gesture and cast a dark, silent pall across your adversaries.
items.name: The "Throat Slit" Taunt
items.webDescription1: Implant a sense of inevitable doom with this vicious and fearsome gesture and cast a dark, silent pall across your adversaries.

items.description: When it is necessary to communicate revulsion and repugnance, no better action conveys it than one of unbridled nausea.
items.name: The "Gag" Reaction
items.webDescription1: When it is necessary to communicate revulsion and repugnance, no better action conveys it than one of unbridled nausea.

items.description: Be offended at everything. You deserve nothing but the highest respect and are above such loutish treatment.
items.name: The "How Dare You?" Reaction
items.webDescription1: Be offended at everything. You deserve nothing but the highest respect and are above such loutish treatment.

items.description: This jovial proclamation towards the heavens is meant to ring across the valleys and hollers, communicating your wild enthusiasm at discovering riches, consummating a betrothal, or finalizing its annulment.
items.name: The "Yeehaw" Reaction
items.webDescription1: This jovial proclamation towards the heavens is meant to ring across the valleys and hollers, communicating your wild enthusiasm at discovering riches, consummating a betrothal, or finalizing its annulment.

items.description: Mimic and mime your lasso skills and playfully pretend to capture and pull an object of affection towards you.
items.name: The 'Get Over Here' Greet
items.webDescription1: Mimic and mime your lasso skills and playfully pretend to capture and pull an object of affection towards you.

items.description: Does someone deserve to be put in their place? The humiliating sound of drawn-out clapping will bereave their very existence.
items.name: The "Slow Clap" Reaction
items.webDescription1: Does someone deserve to be put in their place? The humiliating sound of drawn-out clapping will bereave their very existence.

items.description: Curse the fates and weep with poise, regardless if it is sincere or not.
items.name: The "Weep" Reaction
items.webDescription1: Curse the fates and weep with poise, regardless if it is sincere or not.

items.description: A jovial, good natured guffaw, grinning from ear to ear.
items.name: The 'Jovial Laugh' Reaction
items.webDescription1: A jovial, good natured guffaw, grinning from ear to ear.

items.description: A Southern greeting, exaggerated and heartwarming. Sometimes earnest.
items.name: The "Good to See Ya" Greet
items.webDescription1: A Southern greeting, exaggerated and heartwarming. Sometimes earnest.

items.description: Blow your own trumpet. You are magnificent and everyone around you has a sub-par life.  It’s not egotistic behaviour. It’s just confidence.
items.name: The "Boast" Action
items.webDescription1: Blow your own trumpet. You are magnificent and everyone around you has a sub-par life.  It’s not egotistic behaviour. It’s just confidence.

items.description: Whether hunting animals, catching felons or enduring incessant yammering, signal for some silence.
items.name: The "Hush Your Mouth" Reaction
items.webDescription1: Whether hunting animals, catching felons or enduring incessant yammering, signal for some silence.

items.description: Politely acknowledge friend or foe with this subtle and relaxed wave of the hand.
items.name: The 'Subtle Wave' Greet
items.webDescription1: Politely acknowledge friend or foe with this subtle and relaxed wave of the hand.

items.description: For when you can’t contain your excitement, celebrate by thrusting a fist in the air. Perfect for punctuating the moment at rallies, last minute weddings, or when providing oratory during mob justice.
items.name: The "Hell Yeah" Action
items.webDescription1: For when you can’t contain your excitement, celebrate by thrusting a fist in the air. Perfect for punctuating the moment at rallies, last minute weddings, or when providing oratory during mob justice.

items.description: Vocalize and advertise your acquisition of new territory, search for companionship, or utter loneliness in a primal, prolonged fashion.
items.name: The 'Howl' Action
items.webDescription1: Vocalize and advertise your acquisition of new territory, search for companionship, or utter loneliness in a primal, prolonged fashion.

items.description: Call out with a halloo, reunite with an old friend, or simply thrust yourself into the attention of everyone in your midst.
items.name: The "Hey You!" Greet
items.webDescription1: Call out with a halloo, reunite with an old friend, or simply thrust yourself into the attention of everyone in your midst.

items.description: An aerial delivery of endearment, wanton lust or playful mockery, the blown kiss is sure to arouse or enrage.
items.name: The "Blow Kiss" Action
items.webDescription1: An aerial delivery of endearment, wanton lust or playful mockery, the blown kiss is sure to arouse or enrage.

items.description: An immediate and indignant offer to settle a situation immediately on site through pistol fire or fisticuffs.
items.name: The 'You vs Me' Taunt
items.webDescription1: An immediate and indignant offer to settle a situation immediately on site through pistol fire or fisticuffs.

items.description: A surly, audacious greeting that communicates real bravado and let’s everyone here know who, in fact, is boss.
items.name: The "Tough Guy Nod" Greet
items.webDescription1: A surly, audacious greeting that communicates real bravado and let’s everyone here know who, in fact, is boss.

items.description: When your life hangs precariously in the balance, tug on the heartstrings of your enemies.  Grovel. It may save your life.
items.name: The "Beg for Mercy" Reaction
items.webDescription1: When your life hangs precariously in the balance, tug on the heartstrings of your enemies.  Grovel. It may save your life.

items.description: A reverent bow indicating respect, even if your heart is bathed in wrath.
items.name: The "Respectful Bow" Greet
items.webDescription1: A reverent bow indicating respect, even if your heart is bathed in wrath.

items.description: No deeper humiliation is conveyed than with a long, bony finger pointed at a culprit with a snide demeanor. Infuriate your friends. Confuse your enemies.
items.name: The "Point" Action
items.webDescription1: No deeper humiliation is conveyed than with a long, bony finger pointed at a culprit with a snide demeanor. Infuriate your friends. Confuse your enemies.

items.description: A jaunty greeting for any self-assured citizen caught between doffing their hat and firing their fingers.
items.name: The "Hat Flick" Greet
items.webDescription1: A jaunty greeting for any self-assured citizen caught between doffing their hat and firing their fingers.

items.description: Indulge those around you with a demonstration of your impeccable physique. Will it impress? Possibly. Will it amuse? Certainly.
items.name: The "Flex" Action
items.webDescription1: Indulge those around you with a demonstration of your impeccable physique. Will it impress? Possibly. Will it amuse? Certainly.

items.description: Poke fun at the misfortune of others while celebrating your health and abundance. True joy comes when lording your station over the unfortunate.
items.name: The "You gonna cry?" Taunt
items.webDescription1: Poke fun at the misfortune of others while celebrating your health and abundance. True joy comes when lording your station over the unfortunate.

items.description: Derived from the Ancient Greeks, this timeless gesture will make your enemies bitterly conscious of your dominance, strength and rebellion.
items.name: The "Flip Off" Taunt
items.webDescription1: Derived from the Ancient Greeks, this timeless gesture will make your enemies bitterly conscious of your dominance, strength and rebellion.

items.description: Farcical, boisterous and outrageous, this feigning of a dramatic death is just the thing to amuse a crowd or disparage a person who met an untimely demise at your hand.
items.name: The "I’m Hit" Reaction
items.webDescription1: Farcical, boisterous and outrageous, this feigning of a dramatic death is just the thing to amuse a crowd or disparage a person who met an untimely demise at your hand.

items.description: Feeling gentile? For those who are shy or coy in nature, try this charming way of greeting friends and strangers.
items.name: The "Gentle Wave" Greet
items.webDescription1: Feeling gentile? For those who are shy or coy in nature, try this charming way of greeting friends and strangers.

items.description: This dance was made popular by prospectors celebrating success in mineral extraction or through the overindulgence of banjo music and corn whiskey.
items.name: The "Prospector Jig" Action
items.webDescription1: This dance was made popular by prospectors celebrating success in mineral extraction or through the overindulgence of banjo music and corn whiskey.

items.description: Be bold by demonstrating your courage and goading someone into a blind rage. Bait them, then reel in your catch.
items.name: The "Bring it on" Taunt
items.webDescription1: Be bold by demonstrating your courage and goading someone into a blind rage. Bait them, then reel in your catch.
